title: Luke Nguyens United Kingdom - Series 1 Complete
description:
Luke Nguyen's United Kingdom - Series 1 Complete




In this new series, Luke Nguyen embarks on a culinary exploration around the United Kingdom, unearthing the unique, quirky and mouth-watering delicacies of this historic and fascinating island.

Luke peels back the layers of the UK food identity. With his heritage never too far away, Luke unearths the multicultural diversity that has changed tastebuds in the United Kingdom. From chasing succulent langoustines and sampling Scottish haggis, to learning the secrets of a traditional Cornish pasty, Luke discovers the quirky, delicious and famous dishes that make the UK a unique food landscape.




Original Air Dates: 14-May-2015 to 16-Jul-2015
